<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vendor Approval - VendorHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Background and body styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196F3, #21CBF3);
            color: #fff;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .waiting-container {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        .info-text {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #bbb;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .spinner {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 5px solid transparent;
            border-top: 5px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1.5s linear infinite;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Responsive styling */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .waiting-container {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .message {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .info-text {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="waiting-container">
        <h1>Welcome to VendorHub!</h1>
        <div class="message">
            <p>Your vendor account is under review.</p>
            <p>Please be patient as our admin team verifies your details.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="spinner"></div>

        <div class="info-text">
            <p>VendorHub is a platform designed to connect vendors with businesses and customers. Once approved, you will gain access to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Manage your products and services</li>
                <li>Track your orders and customers</li>
                <li>Benefit from exclusive marketing tools</li>
                <li>And much more!</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="/contact">contact support</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
